    "description": "包含KPOP偶像培养、成长经历的偶像模拟养成类型手游。<br><br>[偶像大师]!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865080/extras/95c991397044c82cd3cf60191530fa7f.poster.avif?t=1755179687\" width=610 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865080/extras/95c991397044c82cd3cf60191530fa7f.webm?t=1755179687\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865080/extras/95c991397044c82cd3cf60191530fa7f.mp4?t=1755179687\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>🔥像现实中培养偶像一样的真实模拟<br>制作人与少女相见，培养并帮助他们成长，作为公司的高管<br>参加公司的经营活动<br>培养偶像公司也能升级！<br>通过我的经营战略，将其培养成人气偶像！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865080/extras/32da36d3cc38a2b1e4ddc4e8edd0338d.poster.avif?t=1755179687\" width=610 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865080/extras/32da36d3cc38a2b1e4ddc4e8edd0338d.webm?t=1755179687\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865080/extras/32da36d3cc38a2b1e4ddc4e8edd0338d.mp4?t=1755179687\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865080/extras/db01fa42929ff7bee7dcd1d6e811c96c.poster.avif?t=1755179687\" width=610 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865080/extras/db01fa42929ff7bee7dcd1d6e811c96c.webm?t=1755179687\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865080/extras/db01fa42929ff7bee7dcd1d6e811c96c.mp4?t=1755179687\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865080/extras/152f57433531e06507b016c9157bffdd.poster.avif?t=1755179687\" width=610 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865080/extras/152f57433531e06507b016c9157bffdd.webm?t=1755179687\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865080/extras/152f57433531e06507b016c9157bffdd.mp4?t=1755179687\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>🎤以3D CG展现的偶像世界<br>引入才华横溢的练习生，打造组合，展开最佳的舞台！<br>在直播舞台，我培养的偶像变成3D登场！<br>用充满生机的3D来展现独属我的组合。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865080/extras/7726ec286a62f547fb792f4c779e43fb.poster.avif?t=1755179687\" width=610 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865080/extras/7726ec286a62f547fb792f4c779e43fb.webm?t=1755179687\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865080/extras/7726ec286a62f547fb792f4c779e43fb.mp4?t=1755179687\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>📈系统的偶像培养管理系统<br>培养成国际偶像的各种系统！<br>通过日程管理、声乐、舞蹈、演技训练，提高偶像的才能和魅力！<br>将其培养成演唱会、电影、电视剧等各领域得到认可的明星！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865080/extras/95c991397044c82cd3cf60191530fa7f.poster.avif?t=1755179687\" width=610 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865080/extras/95c991397044c82cd3cf60191530fa7f.webm?t=1755179687\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865080/extras/95c991397044c82cd3cf60191530fa7f.mp4?t=1755179687\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>💌与我偶像的沟通<br>请与引进的偶像进行沟通吧！基于与偶像们的纽带关系<br>让偶像能力进一步提高。通过【日记】功能与<br>和我偶像的特别故事，SNS图片相遇吧！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865080/extras/d7a6cb1308b86216f91b038bb3e6023c.poster.avif?t=1755179687\" width=610 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865080/extras/d7a6cb1308b86216f91b038bb3e6023c.webm?t=1755179687\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865080/extras/d7a6cb1308b86216f91b038bb3e6023c.mp4?t=1755179687\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>👗通过礼服搭配展现各种各样的协作<br>给偶像的服装、头发颜色、小饰品等各部位进行装扮！<br>每个部分都可以自由修改！让我的偶像变得更加可爱更加漂亮！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865080/extras/c448bfd25676738bdb9f90122903bd27.poster.avif?t=1755179687\" width=610 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865080/extras/c448bfd25676738bdb9f90122903bd27.webm?t=1755179687\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865080/extras/c448bfd25676738bdb9f90122903bd27.mp4?t=1755179687\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>🛏️ 偶像宿舍的装修<br>为了让偶像住的舒适给偶像装修宿舍！<br>房间的各种家具将与偶像产生相互作用，从而有助于休息和缓解疲劳。<br>偶尔我的朋友也会过来玩儿！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865080/extras/811b0f98369be6da057513703ffa8e45.poster.avif?t=1755179687\" width=610 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865080/extras/811b0f98369be6da057513703ffa8e45.webm?t=1755179687\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865080/extras/811b0f98369be6da057513703ffa8e45.mp4?t=1755179687\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>🗳️总选举<br>用户间通过实时比拼，以各地区的投票数为基准计算排名<br>根据排名，可获得各种奖励<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865080/extras/f935bbefb1cc24c6b1f6d50465b5a433.poster.avif?t=1755179687\" width=610 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865080/extras/f935bbefb1cc24c6b1f6d50465b5a433.webm?t=1755179687\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865080/extras/f935bbefb1cc24c6b1f6d50465b5a433.mp4?t=1755179687\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>●其他更多的活动<br>若成功进行偶像培养和公司经营，除训练外还需要很多的事情吧。<br>通过专辑制作，开设以游戏、美食店、料理为主题的频道，运营周边店（快闪店）、晋级考试、粉丝任务等多种任务<br>积累与偶像的好感度，获得股东的信任！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865080/extras/4e01106b08e9b18a4ebba796bfab3ded.poster.avif?t=1755179687\" width=610 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865080/extras/4e01106b08e9b18a4ebba796bfab3ded.webm?t=1755179687\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865080/extras/4e01106b08e9b18a4ebba796bfab3ded.mp4?t=1755179687\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865080/extras/5e95553b35ae6fe362b5c9d17dd9b652.poster.avif?t=1755179687\" width=610 height=342